  <prompt>
    <goal>Create Deploy-SmartTodo.ps1 following the Deploy-EventDetailSidePane.ps1 pattern. Steps: get access token via az CLI, find/create sprk_smarttodo web resource in Dataverse, npm run build in src/solutions/SmartTodo, base64-encode dist/index.html, upload via REST API, publish customizations.</goal>
    <context>
      The SmartTodo Code Page produces a single HTML file via Vite + vite-plugin-singlefile. Deployment
      to Dataverse requires uploading this file as a web resource named sprk_smarttodo. The existing
      Deploy-EventDetailSidePane.ps1 script provides the exact pattern to follow.
    </context>
    <constraints>
      <constraint source="ADR-026">Web resource name must be sprk_smarttodo; single HTML output from Vite build</constraint>
    </constraints>
  </prompt>
